        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2 sm:mt-4 max-w-xl sm:max-w-3xl mx-auto text-base sm:text-xl text-gray-600">
          Découvrez la puissance de l'IA appliquée à la nutrition. Notre technologie avancée 
          révolutionne votre approche de l'alimentation avec une précision scientifique.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
        <!-- AI Feature 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 p-8 group hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Analyse IA Instantanée</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Notre IA analyse instantanément la composition nutritionnelle de vos repas avec une précision de 99,2%. 
            Reconnaissance automatique d'aliments et calculs nutritionnels en temps réel.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-indigo-600 font-medium">
            <span>Précision scientifique</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- AI Feature 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 p-8 group hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Recommandations IA Personnalisées</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Recevez des conseils nutritionnels sur-mesure générés par notre IA. 
            Adaptation continue selon vos objectifs, contraintes et préférences alimentaires.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-purple-600 font-medium">
            <span>Personnalisation totale</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- AI Feature 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 p-8 group hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-teal-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Prédictions IA Intelligentes</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Notre IA prédit vos besoins nutritionnels futurs et anticipe vos carences. 
            Alertes proactives et suggestions d'ajustements avant même que les problèmes n'apparaissent.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-green-600 font-medium">
            <span>Prévention intelligente</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- AI Feature 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 p-8 group hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Assistant IA Conversationnel</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Posez vos questions nutrition à notre IA conversationnelle 24/7. 
            Réponses expertes instantanées, explications détaillées et conseils pratiques.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-blue-600 font-medium">
            <span>Support 24/7</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- AI Feature 5 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 p-8 group hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-red-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Planification IA Adaptive</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Notre IA génère automatiquement vos menus selon vos contraintes (budget, temps, goûts). 
            Plans adaptatifs qui évoluent avec vos résultats et préférences.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-orange-600 font-medium">
            <span>Automatisation complète</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- AI Feature 6 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 p-8 group hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-green-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Motivation IA Comportementale</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Notre IA analyse vos habitudes et déclenche des interventions motivationnelles personnalisées. 
            Psychologie comportementale appliquée pour maximiser votre adhésion.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-teal-600 font-medium">
            <span>Engagement optimisé</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- AI Benefits Section -->
  <div class="py-12 sm:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-10 sm:mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-2 sm:mb-4">
          Pourquoi Choisir une <span class="text-indigo-600">IA Nutritionnelle</span> ?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-xl sm:max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          L'intelligence artificielle révolutionne la nutrition. Découvrez les avantages exclusifs 
          d'un suivi nutritionnel 100% alimenté par l'IA.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 sm:gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Left side - Benefits list -->
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Précision Scientifique</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Notre IA traite des milliers de données nutritionnelles simultanément avec une précision 
                de 99,2%, impossible à atteindre manuellement.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-purple-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 3v1m0 16v1m9-9h-1M4 12H3m15.364 6.364l-.707-.707M6.343 6.343l-.707-.707m12.728 0l-.707.707M6.343 17.657l-.707.707M16 12a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Disponibilité 24/7</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Votre nutritionniste IA ne dort jamais. Conseils, analyses et recommandations 
                disponibles instantanément, à tout moment.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-green-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Apprentissage Continu</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Notre IA s'améliore constamment grâce au machine learning, intégrant les dernières 
                recherches nutritionnelles automatiquement.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Personnalisation Extrême</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Chaque recommandation est unique à votre profil : métabolisme, objectifs, 
                contraintes et préférences analysées par l'IA.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right side - Visual representation -->
        <div class="relative mt-8 lg:mt-0">
